snippet.title: Project Temporality Steam Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam
http://store.steampowered.com/app/290320/
Press Contact
press(@)defrostgames.com

So at last we are ready here with a trailer to show you more of the gameplay of Project Temporality. 

To give you a view of what happens inside the players head inside the game we have gone with a splitscreen display for this trailer.

For more info please visit www.defrostgames.com
